♪ The blond waitresses
take their trays ♪

463
00:21:58,585 --> 00:22:00,854
♪ they spin around,
and they cross the floor ♪

464
00:22:00,888 --> 00:22:02,123
♪ they’ve got the moves

465
00:22:02,155 --> 00:22:03,123
♪ oh, whey, oh

466
00:22:03,156 --> 00:22:04,157
♪ you drop your drink

467
00:22:04,191 --> 00:22:05,459
♪ then they bring you more

468
00:22:05,492 --> 00:22:07,961
♪ all the school kids
so sick of books ♪

469
00:22:07,995 --> 00:22:10,164
♪ they like the punk
and the metal band ♪

470
00:22:10,197 --> 00:22:11,398
♪ when the buzzer rings

471
00:22:11,431 --> 00:22:12,899
♪ oh, whey, oh

472
00:22:12,933 --> 00:22:14,902
♪ they’re walking
like an Egyptian ♪

473
00:22:14,935 --> 00:22:17,037
♪ all the kids
in the marketplace say ♪

474
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:19,272
♪ whey, oh, whey, oh

475
00:22:19,306 --> 00:22:24,077
♪ ay, whey, oh, whey, oh

476
